displayName: Entrance to the Estate of the Profligate Noble

parameters:
Thief Nora: P-Please look! I can see something rolling in
the back.
Clea: We'll take a look at the crystal, please.

Swift Celis: Understood, this place is more dangerous than
the Oros Forest, so be careful.

Swift Celis: I'm also worried if there's a path for the
carriage. If there are any obstacles, please remove them.

Wealthy-looking man: My mother's memento... they took it
from me...
Clea: I will definitely retrieve it for you.

Priestess Sophia: Let's offer our prayers later, so that
they may safely be guided to Terioth.

Mage Relm: How barbaric! To be able to do something like
this so casually...!
Clea: Perhaps they mistook our carriage and attacked us.

Clea: Let's go. This will also be a revenge for these
people.
